                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-982994680" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="982994680">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/likalanyuki/">立花岚雪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">开山之作。图版多且豪华，虽然不是彩页但也很满足了。铜、石兵篇幅多，反而铁兵（汉后）篇幅较少，甲类也不多。关于大马士革、古兵器上纹样研究略有意思。需要注意各类兵器的断代依据。配合亚洲古兵器研究一书阅读风味更佳。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="906850865">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-906850865" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-906850865" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="906850865">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2549129/">马脸</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-03-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">对春秋青铜戈、戟、矛、剑讲的极细，汉代以降论述较少，细分上总觉得还是粗，老先生看的东西还是少了，可惜可惜。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="902330217">
